md:
giải nghĩa từ "pissarro" sang tiếng việt; đưa ra nghĩa tiếng việt theo từ loại và đưa ra câu ví dụ, các từ liên quan.

1. Pissarro (n) - Họa sĩ người Pháp (1830-1903)

* Meaning: Camille Pissarro was a French painter and printmaker.

Example sentence: Camille Pissarro was a key figure in the Impressionist movement.

Related words: painter, printmaker, Impressionist, movement.

2. Pissarro (n) - Con trai của họa sĩ Camille Pissarro

* Meaning: Lucien Pissarro was the son of Camille Pissarro and also a painter.

Example sentence: Lucien Pissarro was a painter and etcher, and the son of Camille Pissarro.

Related words: painter, etcher, son.

Note: There are other people with the surname Pissarro, but the above definitions are the most well-known ones.
